Steps for running the tests:

1. run ../setup-dependencies, which will download all dependencies (google test, poco and simpleopt).
2. run make
3. run ./run, which accepts all command line options of google test plus some custom parameters
	a) --gtest_filter=a regular expression
		for example --gtest_filter=*stat will just run the stat test
	b) --gtest_list_tests
		produces a list of all tests
	c) --keep_capture_files
		if specified will keep all capture files, even if a test does not fail
	d) --gtest_output=xml